v 3
d xhelp -- Tools to create, install and display translated help files
d 
d -xhelp- is an extension to the official -help- command, which provides 
d tools to edit original help files into translated version, pre-packaged
d LLM-translated help files and display them (or the original one when 
d translated version not found).
d 
d KW: workflow
d KW: help system
d 
d Requires: Stata version 9
d
d Version: 1.0
d Distribution-Date: 2026-03-08
d 
d Author:  Yongyi Zeng (Xiamen University, PRC)
d Support: zzyy@xmu.edu.cn
d 

* comments, not be displayed.
* f lines name the files that comprise your package.
* F can force a default-not-installed file to be install to sysdir.
* help net

f xhelp.ado
f xhelp_sthlps.zip
